SECTION 3: THE FIVE OPPOSITION PAIRS

These are the only pairs that produce negation. All other Essence combinations are neutral
and simply express together in the compound.

  VITALIS   <->  VENITAS     Life vs. Entropy
  GRAVITAS  <->  AGILITAS    Weight vs. Speed
  IGNIS     <->  GLACIES     Fire vs. Frost
  CAECITAS  <->  FULGUR      Concealment vs. Discharge
  FORTITAS  <->  ANIMA       Hardening vs. Spirit/Mind

HOW TO DETERMINE NEGATION TIER (read down to first match)

  1. Are BOTH opposing Essences Primary in their respective ingredients?
       YES -> PRIMARY NEGATION. Entire brew collapses. Stop here.

  2. Is either opposing Essence Secondary in its ingredient?
       YES -> SECONDARY NEGATION. Both affected Essences significantly weakened.
              Other Essences in the brew are unaffected. Brew still works.

  3. Is either opposing Essence Tertiary in its ingredient?
       YES -> TERTIARY NEGATION. Minor weakening. Treat as flavor. Brew works normally.

NOTE: Multiple opposition pairs can be active in the same brew. Check all pairs
independently. A brew with one SECONDARY negation and one TERTIARY negation has both
effects. Any single PRIMARY negation collapses the entire brew regardless of everything else.


