SECTION 4: THE INGREDIENT CATALOGUE

ESSENCE TIER KEY
  [P] = Primary      (dominant property; the tasting gives this to anyone)
  [S] = Secondary    (read by a character who has studied the essences)
  [T] = Tertiary     (read by a character who knows the essences cold)

All ingredient Essence listings are drawn from canonical Skyrim properties, mapped
to the system's ten Essences. Effects that do not correspond to any of the ten Essences
(e.g., Waterbreathing, Muffle) are noted as [SPECIAL] — the GM adjudicates these as
unusual Essence expressions on a case-by-case basis.

